Distant Worlds Universe REFRESHED EM Version (DWUR-EM)

Read about all the changes on the wiki: https://github.com/salemonz/DWUR-EM/wiki

/========== About ==========\
Now that Distant Worlds Universe Refreshed is several years old, I am looking to revisit some of the assets and features. This new version of DWUR leans into the expanded capabilities of DWU from Alvek's Expansion Mod. Enjoy!
-- Salemonz

v1.0.3 -- 26 April 2026 -- Rebalanced resources to avoid bottlenecks and bad starts for player/AI empires. Also fixed errors in GameText (thank you CaesarAug!)
v1.0.2 -- 23 April 2026 -- Removed TroopCompartment from all non-troop-transport ship designs across all 46 races.
v1.0.1 -- 17 April 2026 -- Fixed race government preferences. Nine races didn't have access to the right sets of governments for them, based on lore.
